PREAMBLE

This License Agreement ("Agreement") governs the use, modification,
and distribution of the plasXOC Windows Playbook ("the Playbook"),
including all associated scripts, configuration files, batch files,
YAML definitions, and any supplementary materials provided alongside
it. This Agreement is entered into between plasXOC & Solah ("the
Authors") and any individual or entity ("the User") who obtains,
installs, runs, modifies, or distributes the Playbook in any form.

By obtaining, installing, or running the Playbook in any capacity,
the User agrees to be bound by the terms of this Agreement in full.
If the User does not agree to these terms, they must not use the
Playbook in any form.

The Playbook was created with a single principle in mind: Windows
should be free of corporate interference, data harvesting, and
forced behaviour that serves Microsoft rather than the person
sitting at the keyboard. This software is a reflection of that
belief. It is offered free of charge and is intended to remain that
way, permanently and without exception.

