with or referenced by the package.

1.2 "Authors" refers to plasXOC and Solah, the original creators
and current maintainers of the Playbook.

1.3 "User" refers to any individual, group, organisation, or legal
entity that obtains, accesses, installs, executes, modifies, or
distributes the Playbook or any portion thereof.

1.4 "Modified Version" refers to any derivative work based on the
Playbook in which one or more components have been altered, removed,
added to, or combined with other software or content.

1.5 "Distribution" refers to any act of making the Playbook or a
Modified Version available to a third party, whether through direct
transfer, hosting, mirroring, embedding, or any other means.

1.6 "Commercial Use" refers to any use of the Playbook or a
Modified Version in exchange for monetary compensation, goods,
services, subscriptions, or any other form of consideration,
whether direct or indirect.

